{"tid":2393067,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"熱爆Clubhouse app用支那製「聲網」做底 聲音私隱自動送中","createTime":"2021-02-03T08:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T04:39:54.000Z","uid":44209,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec51fcfc632374088c131f9628ffb1dbf3fe0a6","tid":2393067,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"不知道是不是因為多得Elon Musk加持，雖然Clubhouse app只有iOS版本，兼且要有朋友邀請才能加入，但無論在美國甚至乎在香港，都突然引起很大的熱潮。香港不少人都會「開房」，一齊吹水。winandmac Media記者發現Clubhouse app的香港聊天室極多，不少朋友都愛去閒話家常。<br />\n<br />\n不過，亦有人發現Clubhouse <a href=\"http://app使用Agora.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapp%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Agora.io&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjUWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=a5208815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">app使用Agora.io</a>做底層，<a href=\"http://Agora.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAgora.io&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjUWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=9903cb28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Agora.io</a>「聲網」本身總部設於上海，亦即是中國公司。大家都清楚中國公司有幾多是真正民營兼黨無份，而且中國公司根據中國法例，必需保存用戶所有記錄。有專家研究過所有人用緊的Clubhouse app中，有AgoraRtcKit.framework，或多或少確認真的有使用中國聲網的開發工具。有少部份人在Twitter上，擔心用戶登記時會被要求要用電話，有人更會有真名，配合聲音等都是敏感私人資料。而最令人失望的是，Clubhouse作為熱爆的獨角獸，竟然無自己技術，要靠中國聲網。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Clubhouse爆紅後，<a href=\"http://中國公司Agora.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8Agora.io&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjUWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=86e9890c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">中國公司Agora.io</a>的股價亦狂升。我們winandmac Media記者曾嘗試與Clubhouse app傳媒公關聯絡，查詢用戶聲音會否「送中」，但在本文章發表時並無回覆。<br />\n<br />\n香港IT企業創辦人Innopage負責人李勁華接受我們winandmac Media記者訪問時指出，其實上得網就難以不留痕跡，「諗清楚先講，始終係公開平台，大家都聽到」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2021/02/clubhouse-app-using-chinese-company-agora-raises-privacy-issues/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2021%2F02%2Fclubhouse-app-using-chinese-company-agora-raises-privacy-issues%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjUWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=31edfeca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2021/02/clubhouse-app-using-chinese-company-agora-raises-privacy-issues/</a>"},{"pid":"5818c56ab2c73fc734dceab5dcb702e6f0445152","tid":2393067,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"好彩連登冇人用呢個支那app<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ddfc2892d9421e50faa0d16b17422f5b95d5dc","tid":2393067,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"用大數據重建聲紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1c90ead51d3bd97267f88b1ef8b3db12fcaa21","tid":2393067,"uid":141387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"好彩我無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔又贏"},{"pid":"aeb627f5dba0ee0a2086e830b7681cc250ccc7cf","tid":2393067,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c1c90ead51d3bd97267f88b1ef8b3db12fcaa21","tid":2393067,"uid":141387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"好彩我無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔又贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"留意到自己圈子開始有人吹奏"}]}